		<a name="twoButton"/><h3>Two Button Mouse with Scroll Wheel and Keyboard</h3>
		<table width="100%" border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
			<tbody>
				<tr>
					<td valign="top" width="142">
						<strong>Pan:</strong>
					</td>
					<td width="586">
						<ul>
							<li>Left mouse button click &amp; drag - all directions</li>
							<li>Single click left button to center screen</li>
							<li>Left/right/up/down arrows on the keyboard<br /></li>
						</ul>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td valign="top" width="142">
						<strong>Zoom:</strong>
					</td>
					<td>
						<ul>
							<li>Use the scroll wheel on the mouse to zoom in/out</li>
							<li>Middle mouse button/scroll wheel - click and drag - up and down</li>
							<li>Double click left/right button to zoom in/out and center screen</li>
							<li>Ctrl + up/down arrows on the keyboard<br /></li>
						</ul>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td valign="top" width="142">
						<strong>Tilt: </strong>
					</td>
					<td>
						<ul>
							<li>Right mouse button click &amp; drag - up and down</li>
							<li>'Page Up' and 'Page Down' or shift + up/down arrows on the keyboard<br /></li>
						</ul>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td valign="top">
						<strong>Rotate: </strong>
					</td>
					<td>
						<ul>
							<li>
								Right mouse button click &amp; drag - left and right<br />
								Note: Crossing the top and bottom half of the screen while
								rotating will change direction.
							</li>
							<li>Shift + left/right arrows on the keyboard</li>
						</ul>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td valign="top">
						<strong>Stop Movement: </strong>
					</td>
					<td>
						<ul>
							<li>Spacebar</li>
						</ul>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td valign="top">
						<strong>Reset Heading: </strong>
					</td>
					<td>
						<ul>
							<li>N</li>
						</ul>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td valign="top">
						<strong>Reset Heading/Tilt: </strong>
					</td>
					<td>
						<ul>
							<li>R</li>
						</ul>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
